705218f-c.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - 19th Street (East)
705218f-c.text:
(1)
King's Highway, south side, between East 19th Street and Ocean Ave.,
showing a barn on the H.R. Wyckoff farm.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, another view.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)  The same, looking south from King's Highway, showing the H.R. Wyckoff house facing East 19th Street in the background. The barn was demolished in 1923.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
